{"tid":44571,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母！你做乜撞鳩我？","createTime":"2016-12-18T11:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T08:06:12.000Z","uid":6836,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02422cc5b09c91eaf3e4f49fb7c1a519807ae874","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"「我屌你老母！你做乜撞鳩我？」一名濃妝豔抹既女仔指住我黎鬧。<br />\n<br />\n「Sorry，我唔小心&hellip;」係銅鑼灣SOGO入面咁多人，撞親人都幾唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n我撞完之後，稍稍打量下眼前呢位女子。穿住件緊身綠色既毛織背心，加條褸屌裙同埋superstar既經典金章。上有微波爐，下有一碌竹。<br />\n<br />\n兩隻字──幾索。<br />\n<br />\n「乜撚野唔小心呀？你中出完人係唔係又同人講唔小心射左入去呀？」佢惡劣既態度終係無改，仲要句句串到衡。<br />\n<br />\n佢大聲夾惡既態度吸引唔少途人望過黎，話曬呢度係SOGO，星期六日無人就假啦。<br />\n<br />\n「我只係撞左一下姐&hellip;&hellip;」 我當下除左感到無奈之外，都係無奈。<br />\n<br />\n「咩撞一下呀！你撞到我個波呀屌你！」佢推一推我肩膀。<br />\n<br />\n圍觀既人嘩然，「哇，撞人個波都有。」之類既聲音好似開咪咁，超大聲傳黎傳去。<br />\n<br />\n我望一望佢個波，得罪講句，一啲波路都無&hellip;&hellip;咩感覺都無喎姐姐。<br />\n<br />\n「望乜撚呀你！」佢仲好嬲咁講。儘管佢著曬緊身衫，好努力咁show俾人睇佢驕傲既身材，但事實就係事實，駁唔到。<br />\n<br />\n「無呀。」我死盯住佢個波黎望，望到個肺添啦，都望唔到啲咩出黎。<br />\n<br />\n「你仲話無！？」佢用手遮住自己心口。<br />\n<br />\n「你依家撞到我，仲撞到埋我個波，點計先？」佢拉住我隻手，近距離咁望住我。<br />\n<br />\n我眼見佢啲妝成寸厚，見到都唔開胃。<br />\n<br />\n我開始頂唔順佢強勢既攻擊，有咩好點算姐，撞一撞個波姐，洗唔洗以身相許呀？<br />\n<br />\n咁多人望住曬，我已經覺得幾無面下，「痴線！」<br />\n<br />\n我甩開左佢隻手，拋低左呢一句，好瀟灑咁轉身走。<br />\n<br />\n好死唔死，佢條仔岩岩返到黎。佢捉左條仔過黎，「佢蝦我！」指住我。<br />\n<br />\n佢條仔身材槐梧，都幾大隻下。相對之下，我係比較好恰嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n條仔聞言，望住我，用眼掃一掃我全身，知道可以打得贏我，就講：「做咩恰鳩我條女？」佢兇鳩我。<br />\n<br />\n「我&hellip;&hellip;」當下真係覺得幾委屈下，又俾佢嚇一嚇。<br />\n<br />\n好似全部都夾埋黎恰我咁，人多蝦仁小。<br />\n<br />\n真係，我俾條仔兇疾左，忍唔住喊左出黎。<br />\n<br />\n「你喊呀？」條女同條仔異口同聲咁問。佢地先係驚訝，之後就係度竊笑。<br />\n<br />\n「嘻嘻，喊喎佢！」各種笑聲此起彼落。<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n鐘意既歡迎留個正皮同留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會係我作落去既動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ead07fafabb28e5b5f7abac493c699e76fdfaa4","tid":44571,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母撞到我部電話吧"},{"pid":"50e4578fba757284f93ae420c565ba2fa35e6fbb","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"第一章 【屌老母】<br />\n<br />\n「喂！跟住呢跟住呢？無啦？」森仔好激動咁講。<br />\n<br />\n「無啦！唔係你仲想點？」我嬲嬲地咁講。<br />\n<br />\n「唔係呢治仔，老實講，你喊嗰一野真係好拎好笑，哈哈哈！」佢既笑聲停唔到。<br />\n<br />\n算！我都慣架啦，呢班仆街成日都笑鳩我架啦，笑我鵪鶉咁呀嘛。<br />\n<br />\n「好心你咪咁啦！人地俾人拍片擺上Youtube已經好慘架啦。」呀亮幫我出頭，但佢幫我出頭似係踩多我兩腳咁。<br />\n<br />\n森仔笑得仲大聲，「哈哈哈，真係好撚柒！點解可以咁柒？」<br />\n<br />\n我緊握雙拳，好想打爆呢班柒頭皮！！！<br />\n<br />\n呀亮見勢頭唔對路，連忙講：「咪講啦，再講佢嬲啦！」<br />\n<br />\n森仔扮曬正經咁行過黎搭住我膊頭，「如果沙皮係度呀，串得你仲甘呀！」<br />\n<br />\n佢講得又幾有道理，沙皮份人都幾嬲打下，佢係度既話，就算我嬲都阻唔到佢。因為佢會嬲埋一份，唔好惹架佢。<br />\n<br />\n「係呢？你做乜野無啦啦去SOGO既？」呀亮突破盲點。"},{"pid":"d8015dfc5314865fa489edfb4150a48188b80198","tid":44571,"uid":3744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"快手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e4103539d4f92921b7b788bc4cba49c703599c","tid":44571,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635c1b63ecb2e0421893c5a04d7cbc5e334fc524","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"我死都唔會話去SOGO睇高達模型，一陣又會俾佢地串我毒到出汁架啦。<br />\n<br />\n「無野呀，買野姐。」我hea道。<br />\n<br />\n「買咩呀？」森仔打蛇隨棍上。<br />\n<br />\n「關你咩事姐！」一句撻埋去，等佢無聲出。「係呢，沙皮呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「睇佢個死款咪又係瞓過龍唔黎返學，黎！我地去食餐好，Happy下，唔好唔開心！」都係呀亮識得安慰人。<br />\n<br />\n「咪係！」森仔係側邊附和道，算佢有返啲人性。<br />\n<br />\n我地依家係lunch time時間，不嬲我地幾個都會出去食飯既，今日亦都唔例外。<br />\n<br />\n我地相安無事咁行出課室，行行下，「唔得，諗起真係覺得好好笑，撞到人地個波係咩感覺呀？正唔正呀？有無扯旗呀哈哈？」<br />\n<br />\n森仔突然爆笑，捂住個肚，係咁揮手。<br />\n<br />\n森仔笑住咁彈一彈我條J，「喂！痛呀！」我喝停佢。<br />\n<br />\n「又真係無扯旗喎，勁呀。」做左個讚好既手勢。<br />\n<br />\n佢見我無反應，嬲爆爆咁既樣，就自動收皮。<br />\n<br />\n「乖，一陣幫你含返佢囉。」佢既厚面皮都幾世界級。<br />\n<br />\n「痴撚線。」我回敬佢一句粗口。<br />\n<br />\n已經夠曬黑仔，頭頭碰著黑，仲要俾人咁樣串法，唔嬲就假。<br />\n<br />\n我低頭安撫下我既子孫根，無留意轉角位迎來一場風暴&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我稱之為──「乳散革命」<br />\n<br />\n砰！<br />\n<br />\n「哇&hellip;&hellip;又邊鬼個撞我呀！」我聽到一陣驚呼。<br />\n<br />\n我額頭傳陣陣既劇痛，呢下撞得都幾重手下。我摸住自己個額頭，睇下撞親邊個。心諗：做乜呢排成日撞到人呀&hellip;&hellip;？<br />\n<br />\n細看之下，睇黎我撞親個靚女喎，整體黎講幾唔錯。"},{"pid":"61e59f28964e7855dd15b9ac756f04d482ab70a0","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:29:16.000Z","msg":"「Sorry呀，我唔小心&hellip;」我講都未講完，就已經俾人串。<br />\n<br />\n「咩唔小心呀，你會唔會殺完人同人講唔小心呀？」<br />\n<br />\n等陣！咁熟既呢句？個語氣都好熟，係邊度聽過呢？一時醒唔起。<br />\n<br />\n但畢竟係我撞到人，我理虧既，仲要當住班兄弟面前，點都要有返啲風度。<br />\n<br />\n「 Sorry呀，你無事呀嘛？」我有禮貌咁講。<br />\n<br />\n「Sorry大曬呀？你問黎都係廢話！你係咪想人答你無事呀白痴？撞到人點會無事呀！用下你個腦啦&hellip;&hellip;再唔用生銹啦！扮曬野咁！」佢咄咄逼人，佢仲摸緊自己額頭。<br />\n<br />\n摸一摸，然後係條校服裙入面拎左塊境出黎，照下自己有無事先。<br />\n<br />\n係我隔黎既呀亮同埋森仔全程見住曬，忍唔住係度偷笑。呢兩條花生友&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n側邊行過既人都開始注意到我地，呢個畫面似層相識&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n佢地聽到呢句之後笑住咁行過黎食花生。<br />\n<br />\n『哇有好戲睇呀！』<br />\n『食花生先&hellip;&hellip;』<br />\n『毒撚大戰C班霸王花呀！』<br />\n『有無花生呀！拎定出黎啦喂！』<br />\n<br />\n「唔係&hellip;&hellip;咁我除左邊Sorry都唔知點做好&hellip;」我喃喃地道。<br />\n<br />\n「好彩無毀容姐&hellip;咩事都無咩事都無。」佢對住塊鏡講得起勁。<br />\n<br />\n「咩呀？你頭先講咩？」佢抬起頭望一望我。唔望仲好，一望就仆街啦。<br />\n<br />\n「原來又係你！上次係SOGO撞完個波，依家又黎撞我額頭？」佢越鬧越大聲，越鬧越興奮。"},{"pid":"a5e3218f4c3b23194cc2c637e39c68809d1a9ad5","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"今晚再更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49680d1657e3930cf0b533f679a4c2ba320cb162","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:05:56.000Z","msg":"無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48b755ee1780ad92b3b009d8f37f84e61288046","tid":44571,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"有人看呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6214d43400858459f1d0a7e1b0dd8338eb86601","tid":44571,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"文呀文呀<br />\n文呀文呀"},{"pid":"071a793be900c0ab3d5c3ef2c85a77245b492185","tid":44571,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"805b3de32fd300e6127121665f753abcb87623bd","tid":44571,"uid":60363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"出文啦屌<br />\nBTW我係樓主就打柒個八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fd0dc130ace55ae7e725d133c58da9b8de6422","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"等一陣再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4cc1956fceff3bca5f900dbf36e5e06922ae42","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出文啦屌<br />\nBTW我係樓主就打柒個八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c52eb5fe529cb3f6948b7af2a1be25e7c01eefc","tid":44571,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536354d5b17dd7198d6a44ff09cc4029d618cf7e","tid":44571,"uid":17354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3cb434e8a22c1f54cf5a8d536155de738b40e1","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"我呆左一呆，仔細望下佢。的確佢無濃妝豔抹，戴上一副圓碌碌既眼鏡，更添幾分可愛。<br />\n<br />\n但我可以話你知，佢一定唔化妝靚過化妝！<br />\n<br />\n『哇！原來就係佢地呀？』<br />\n『上左Youtube嗰兩個呢，估唔到佢地係我地學校架喔！』<br />\n<br />\n圍觀既人越黎越多，搞到我都唔知點好&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「估唔到我地學校出左個喊包。」佢一臉鄙視既模樣。<br />\n<br />\n頂你好講唔講講呢樣&hellip;&hellip;全場每人發出小小既竊笑聲，都可以變成演唱會般既喝采聲。<br />\n<br />\n「喂&hellip;&hellip;你！」我諗唔到咩野駁佢，畢竟我口才真係唔好，如果唔係點會俾人恰？<br />\n<br />\n「你你你你&hellip;你咩姐！」佢不忿，「我同你有咩仇呀，撞完一次又一次！」佢直接走過黎揪起我衫領。<br />\n<br />\n我俾佢嚇一嚇，因為佢真係成個人揪高左我。第一，佢細細粒咁，我高佢成個頭。第二，佢弱質纖纖咁，咁有力揪起個？<br />\n<br />\n「停，有咩事都好，唔好郁手！」呀亮見風頭火勢，一個箭步就衝左出黎。<br />\n<br />\n「你又老幾呀！？」呀亮捉住佢隻手，但好明顯都俾佢個氣勢震懾左。<br />\n<br />\n「小姐，只係唔小心撞左你一下姐，無謂小事化大呀？」呀亮特登講重「小事化大」呢四隻字。<br />\n<br />\n「好！咁你地諗個賠罪方法俾我，就當無數。」<br />\n<br />\n挑你老尾！成個大佬款，呢道氣真係啃唔落。<br />\n<br />\n「屌你老尾，撞你一下係咪要以身相許呀？」我頂佢唔順，逼上梁山，發揮出我內在既潛能。我後來諗返都唔明點解自己咁大勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n『咪係！』其中一個花生友幫我平反，但好細聲，走住黎屌嗰類。<br />\n<br />\n「妖！就算係呀，睇你個死款都唔敢架啦！」<br />\n<br />\n「頭先邊個講粗口？」一把粗壯既男人聲從後傳黎。<br />\n<br />\n『壯Sir！』眾人齊聲道。<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦，咁多條友唔黎，係黎呢條咸濕佬。<br />\n<br />\n佢一黎到，全場安靜曬。因為其他人見到老師黎，已經走撚曬。"},{"pid":"a56c95b5eadc18fc09b4cf7b6090faa8e99cb0db","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣出文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2711ba10a0f9cc169b669c253a3a86102ccb2977","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"負皮既可唔可以留低個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8280c7a3404e49e558d742ddffe9e39295358f4","tid":44571,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:07:50.000Z","msg":"新故？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n負皮我估係因為篇文嘅標題引左啲唔想睇故嘅巴打入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcad7c0bb1fc12f8295ac9ae9745a20efa408bd","tid":44571,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新故？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n負皮我估係因為篇文嘅標題引左啲唔想睇故嘅巴打入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補番條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/44541/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/44541/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"f99cba18ce9bf7904586bb4bd6f422005bc2688c","tid":44571,"uid":64898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:12:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5a2c1347006828c57bc8743fbfc4a6c26ff72f16","tid":44571,"uid":6836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新故？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n負皮我估係因為篇文嘅標題引左啲唔想睇故嘅巴打入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後我都覺得到Sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔應該咁樣呃人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我見之前啲故都係咁，所以咪照板煮碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />